title: Ep. 38 :: Time To Take Profits
itunes:title: Time To Take Profits
description: Frank breaks down earnings and tells us if this rally is sustainable. Rich Suttmeier, chief market strategist at Valuengine.com, talks about the future of our banking system and predicts Dow 8,500 by next year.
